title: Loungevity djs presents, Dj Sly [Downtempo,Dub,Electronica,Loung
description:
Loungevity djs presents, Dj Sly [Downtempo,Dub,Electronica,Lounge].

After 13 years playing in the main room this cd shows Dj Sly taking somewhat a change of style and pace to produce a cd suitable for the chillout room.

The following cd is a live recording of the set played at the BRICKYARD club in carlisle, although downtempo the room was rocking by the end of the set,showing Sly can move a dancefloor whatever style he plays!

Keep checking my page for future Loungevity dj releases from the U.K underground free party scene.

Enjoy...would love to hear you;re comments....
